OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777299067
OL,3,CPc was driving on wrong side of road
OL,4,Cat 60mph before hitting woman, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FA police officer responding to an
OL,8,Femergency call was driving on the
OL,9,Fwrong side of the road at 60mph before
OL,10,Fhitting a woman, a court has heard.
OL,12,FThames Valley Police officer Philip
OL,13,FDuthie is charged with causing death
OL,14,Fby careless driving after colliding
OL,15,Fwith pedestrian Kimberley Cameron on
OL,16,F16 April 2021, Westminster
OL,17,FMagistrates' Court heard on Monday.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
