FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777299067
OL,3,CPc was driving on wrong side of road
OL,4,Cat 60mph before hitting woman, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThe prosecution told the court in the
OL,8,Flead up to the collision, the officer
OL,9,Fhad been driving on the wrong side of
OL,10,Fthe road at 60mph in a 40mph zone.
OL,12,FHis view had been obstructed by a van
OL,13,Fas Ms Cameron crossed the road.
OL,15,FThe Independent Officer for Police
OL,16,FConduct, which has previously
OL,17,Finvestigated the case, said the 27-
OL,18,Fyear-old victim died at the scene in
OL,19,FAylesbury in Buckinghamshire.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
