PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777299067
OL,3,CPc was driving on wrong side of road
OL,4,Cat 60mph before hitting woman, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FAt the brief hearing, the 41-year-old
OL,8,Felected for his case to be heard by a
OL,9,Fjudge and jury at a crown court.
OL,11,FDistrict Judge Michael Snow released
OL,12,FDuthie, of Chappell Way in Leighton
OL,13,FBuzzard, on unconditional bail ahead
OL,14,Fof his next appearance at the Old
OL,15,FBailey on May 26.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
